WEBVTT

00:00:05.399 --> 00:00:07.201
♪ YOUR MOVE, YOUR MOVE,
YOUR MOVE ♪

00:00:07.201 --> 00:00:09.436
♪YOUR MOVE, YOUR MOVE ♪

00:00:15.209 --> 00:00:17.311
♪ YU-GI-OH, YU-GI ♪

00:00:38.365 --> 00:00:41.702
IT'S TIME
TO D-D-D-DUEL!

00:00:55.716 --> 00:00:58.319
♪ YU-GI-OH! ♪

00:01:03.924 --> 00:01:05.893
Boy: I KNOW YOU WON,

00:01:05.893 --> 00:01:07.695
BUT YOU CAN'T
CHANGE THE RULES.

00:01:07.695 --> 00:01:08.796
IT'S NOT FAIR.

00:01:08.796 --> 00:01:10.564
"IT'S NOT FAIR!"

00:01:10.564 --> 00:01:11.865
THAT'S LOSER TALK,
CHUMP!

00:01:11.865 --> 00:01:13.467
THIS CARD
IS WORTHLESS!

00:01:13.467 --> 00:01:15.703
B-B-BUT BATTLE
CITY RULES STATE

00:01:15.703 --> 00:01:18.472
THAT YOU ONLY GET
MY ONE RAREST CARD
IF YOU WIN.

00:01:18.472 --> 00:01:20.374
YEAH? WELL, I'M
MAKING MY OWN RULES!

00:01:20.374 --> 00:01:22.509
NOW, GIVE ME
THE TWO RAREST CARDS

00:01:22.509 --> 00:01:24.445
IN YOUR DUELING DECK
AND FAST!

00:01:24.445 --> 00:01:26.113
TWO CARDS?
COME ON.

00:01:26.113 --> 00:01:27.414
GIVE 'EM UP!

00:01:27.414 --> 00:01:28.782
[WHISTLE BLOWS]

00:01:28.782 --> 00:01:30.117
HUH?

00:01:30.117 --> 00:01:31.852
DUELING FOUL!

00:01:31.852 --> 00:01:33.587
HUH? HEY,
BEAT IT, JUNIOR.

00:01:33.587 --> 00:01:35.022
"JUNIOR?"
YOU'RE TALKING

00:01:35.022 --> 00:01:36.357
TO THE OFFICIAL
COMMISSIONER

00:01:36.357 --> 00:01:37.992
FOR THE BATTLE CITY
TOURNAMENT.

00:01:37.992 --> 00:01:40.227
I WILL SETTLE ANY AND ALL
DUELING DISPUTES.

00:01:40.227 --> 00:01:41.328
AND WHEN IT COMES
TO THE RULES,

00:01:41.328 --> 00:01:42.763
WHAT I SAY GOES.

00:01:42.763 --> 00:01:44.064
DO I MAKE
MYSELF CLEAR?

00:01:44.064 --> 00:01:46.567
I'LL KEEP THAT IN MIND.
NOW, GET LOST!

00:01:46.567 --> 00:01:48.102
IF YOU WANT TO STAY
IN THIS TOURNAMENT,

00:01:48.102 --> 00:01:50.004
YOU'RE GONNA HAVE
TO DO WHAT I SAY!

00:01:50.004 --> 00:01:51.405
OR WHAT?

00:01:51.405 --> 00:01:53.907
Kaiba: OR YOU'LL HAVE
TO DEAL WITH ME.

00:01:53.907 --> 00:01:55.476
WHAT DID YOU SAY?

00:01:59.413 --> 00:02:00.714
HEY, BRO!

00:02:00.714 --> 00:02:02.549
S-SETO KAIBA!

00:02:02.549 --> 00:02:04.451
WHEN YOU SPEAK
TO MY BROTHER THAT WAY,

00:02:04.451 --> 00:02:05.619
YOU DISHONOR ME

00:02:05.619 --> 00:02:06.987
AND THE BATTLE CITY
TOURNAMENT.

00:02:06.987 --> 00:02:08.055
AND BESIDES,

00:02:08.055 --> 00:02:10.491
I HAVE VERY LITTLE
PATIENCE FOR BULLIES.

00:02:10.491 --> 00:02:12.192
WHAT'S YOUR PROBLEM?

00:02:14.995 --> 00:02:18.899
IT'S TIME YOU LEARNED
TO SHOW SOME RESPECT.

00:02:18.899 --> 00:02:19.900
WHOA!

00:02:19.900 --> 00:02:21.235
WHOA, AMAZING!

00:02:21.235 --> 00:02:23.137
WHAT'S UP WITH ALL
THESE RARE CARDS?

00:02:23.137 --> 00:02:25.873
I CHALLENGE YOU
TO A DUEL HERE AND NOW,

00:02:25.873 --> 00:02:27.641
WITH ONE CONDITION:

00:02:27.641 --> 00:02:29.310
YOU MUST USE
THESE RARE CARDS

00:02:29.310 --> 00:02:31.979
TO BOOST THE DUELING POWER
OF YOUR PATHETIC DECK.

00:02:31.979 --> 00:02:35.282
[LAUGHING]
YOU'RE SURE ABOUT THIS?

00:02:38.786 --> 00:02:41.755
WITH ALL THESE RARE CARDS
AND MY SKILL,

00:02:41.755 --> 00:02:43.490
THERE'S NO WAY I'LL LOSE.

00:02:43.490 --> 00:02:45.125
WATCH OUT, KAIBA.

00:02:45.125 --> 00:02:47.761
YOU'RE SETTING
YOURSELF UP FOR A FALL!

00:02:47.761 --> 00:02:49.496
[CHUCKLES]

00:02:49.496 --> 00:02:51.065
HUH?

00:02:51.065 --> 00:02:52.499
IT'S TIME TO DUEL!

00:02:52.499 --> 00:02:53.834
HUH.

00:02:53.834 --> 00:02:56.370
I JUST NEED TO PLAY
A SINGLE CARD

00:02:56.370 --> 00:02:58.839
TO TEACH YOU
A LESSON YOU
WON'T FORGET!

00:03:00.574 --> 00:03:03.243
I SUMMON OBELISK
THE TORMENTOR!

00:03:03.243 --> 00:03:04.945
ATTACK NOW!

00:03:04.945 --> 00:03:06.814
NO! NO!

00:03:15.456 --> 00:03:16.857
[GROANING]

00:03:16.857 --> 00:03:20.060
I'VE NEVER SEEN A CARD
THAT POWERFUL.

00:03:20.060 --> 00:03:22.262
NOW I'LL USE
MY EGYPTIAN GOD CARD

00:03:22.262 --> 00:03:23.630
ON A REAL OPPONENT.

00:03:23.630 --> 00:03:24.932
LET'S FIND YUGI.

00:03:24.932 --> 00:03:26.467
WHOA.

00:03:26.467 --> 00:03:28.302
HEH! <i>NOW</i>
WHO'S THE LOSER?

00:03:31.805 --> 00:03:34.308
Kaiba, thinking: NO ONE MESSES
WITH MY LITTLE BROTHER,

00:03:34.308 --> 00:03:36.610
ESPECIALLY WITH
AN EGYPTIAN GOD CARD

00:03:36.610 --> 00:03:37.678
IN MY DECK.

00:03:37.678 --> 00:03:39.146
IF MY PLAN WORKED,

00:03:39.146 --> 00:03:41.615
THE OTHER TWO CARDS
SHOULD BE HERE IN BATTLE CITY.

00:03:41.615 --> 00:03:45.185
I JUST NEED TO FIND OUT WHERE
SO I CAN WIN THEM.

00:03:45.185 --> 00:03:47.588
WHEN I GET HOLD OF ALL 3
OF THESE UNSTOPPABLE

00:03:47.588 --> 00:03:49.256
EGYPTIAN GOD MONSTERS,

00:03:49.256 --> 00:03:52.393
NOT EVEN YUGI WILL
BE ABLE TO DEFEAT ME.

00:03:52.393 --> 00:03:55.629
ONCE AGAIN, I'LL BE
THE NUMBER-ONE DUELIST
IN THE WORLD!

00:03:55.629 --> 00:03:57.030
[LAUGHING]

00:04:00.033 --> 00:04:01.135
HMM.

00:04:01.135 --> 00:04:03.404
SO, OBELISK THE TORMENTOR
HAS BEEN PLAYED?

00:04:03.404 --> 00:04:04.471
YES.

00:04:04.471 --> 00:04:06.540
MOMENTS AGO
IN BATTLE CITY, MARIK.

00:04:06.540 --> 00:04:08.909
AND WE'VE IDENTIFIED
THE CARD'S OWNER.

00:04:08.909 --> 00:04:10.911
SETO KAIBA.

00:04:10.911 --> 00:04:11.912
HEH HEH HEH!

00:04:11.912 --> 00:04:12.980
OF COURSE.

00:04:12.980 --> 00:04:15.082
HOW DID YOU
KNOW, SIR?

00:04:15.082 --> 00:04:17.050
IT'S QUITE SIMPLE.

00:04:17.050 --> 00:04:19.253
ISHIZU CONSPIRES
AGAINST ME.

00:04:19.253 --> 00:04:22.489
SHE GAVE KAIBA
THAT CARD TO STOP ME.

00:04:22.489 --> 00:04:25.259
NOW WE'RE BOTH
AFTER THE CARDS.

00:04:25.259 --> 00:04:27.127
[THINKING]
I SHOULD HAVE
KNOWN ISHIZU

00:04:27.127 --> 00:04:29.496
WAS BEHIND
THIS WHOLE TOURNAMENT.

00:04:29.496 --> 00:04:32.499
SHE'S BEEN TRYING
TO STAND IN MY WAY

00:04:32.499 --> 00:04:36.069
EVER SINCE I DECIDED
TO TAKE WHAT IS RIGHTFULLY MINE.

00:04:36.069 --> 00:04:39.506
[ALOUD]
NOW OPEN THE LID,
MY SERVANT.

00:04:39.506 --> 00:04:40.908
EXCELLENT.

00:04:43.177 --> 00:04:44.945
UNLOCK THE SAFE.

00:04:46.046 --> 00:04:49.016
[LAUGHING]

00:04:49.016 --> 00:04:50.517
THERE IT IS!

00:04:50.517 --> 00:04:52.519
THE WINGED DRAGON OF RA!

00:04:52.519 --> 00:04:54.388
THAT MAKES TWO.

00:04:54.388 --> 00:04:56.123
ONE MORE EGYPTIAN GOD CARD,

00:04:56.123 --> 00:04:58.091
AND I'LL BE UNSTOPPABLE!

00:04:58.091 --> 00:05:00.627
DON'T TAKE ANOTHER STEP!

00:05:00.627 --> 00:05:02.362
ISHIZU!

00:05:02.362 --> 00:05:03.730
BROTHER!

00:05:03.730 --> 00:05:05.365
MY MILLENNIUM NECKLACE
WARNED ME

00:05:05.365 --> 00:05:07.935
YOU WOULD BETRAY ME,
AND INDEED YOU HAVE.

00:05:07.935 --> 00:05:11.472
5,000 YEARS AGO,
OUR FAMILY SWORE

00:05:11.472 --> 00:05:13.106
TO PROTECT
THE PHARAOH'S TOMB

00:05:13.106 --> 00:05:14.441
UNTIL HIS RETURN.

00:05:14.441 --> 00:05:16.343
WHO KNEW THAT
THE GREATEST THREAT

00:05:16.343 --> 00:05:18.178
WOULD COME
FROM ONE OF OUR OWN?

00:05:18.178 --> 00:05:20.581
WHY SHOULD I
PROTECT HIM?

00:05:20.581 --> 00:05:22.349
I'M CLAIMING WHAT
SHOULD HAVE BEEN MINE

00:05:22.349 --> 00:05:24.184
FROM THE VERY
BEGINNING, SISTER!

00:05:24.184 --> 00:05:27.621
SOON, INSTEAD OF
GUARDING THE PHARAOH,

00:05:27.621 --> 00:05:29.256
I'LL INHERIT
HIS STRENGTH!

00:05:29.256 --> 00:05:31.825
MY DESTINY LIES
IN THE CARDS...

00:05:31.825 --> 00:05:34.161
THE 3 EGYPTIAN GOD
CARDS.

00:05:34.161 --> 00:05:36.763
IF YOU WANT TO CARRY OUT
THIS MADNESS,

00:05:36.763 --> 00:05:40.767
YOU'RE GOING TO HAVE TO
FIND THE LAST CARD.

00:05:40.767 --> 00:05:42.402
I'M WARNING YOU!

00:05:42.402 --> 00:05:44.705
YOU'D USE
YOUR MILLENNIUM ROD

00:05:44.705 --> 00:05:46.940
ON YOUR OWN FLESH
AND BLOOD, MARIK?

00:05:46.940 --> 00:05:49.910
IF YOU CONTINUE
TO STAND IN MY WAY,

00:05:49.910 --> 00:05:52.679
THEN YES, I'LL HAVE TO.

00:05:59.319 --> 00:06:00.387
[THINKING] HMM!

00:06:00.387 --> 00:06:01.755
I KNOW MY SISTER

00:06:01.755 --> 00:06:04.525
GAVE THE THIRD
EGYPTIAN GOD CARD
TO SETO KAIBA.

00:06:04.525 --> 00:06:06.793
SHE USED
HER MILLENNIUM NECKLACE

00:06:06.793 --> 00:06:09.363
TO FORESEE THE EVENTS
OF BATTLE CITY.

00:06:09.363 --> 00:06:12.966
ISHIZU KNEW IF SHE GAVE
OBELISK THE TORMENTOR
TO KAIBA,

00:06:12.966 --> 00:06:15.202
HE'D THROW A TOURNAMENT
OUT OF GREED

00:06:15.202 --> 00:06:17.471
TO OBTAIN THE OTHER
EGYPTIAN GOD CARDS.

00:06:17.471 --> 00:06:19.840
BUT KAIBA HAS LITTLE
UNDERSTANDING

00:06:19.840 --> 00:06:21.208
OF THEIR TRUE STRENGTH,

00:06:21.208 --> 00:06:22.509
AND ONCE I HAVE
THEM ALL,

00:06:22.509 --> 00:06:24.411
THE POWER OF THE PHARAOH
WILL BE MINE!

00:06:24.411 --> 00:06:25.879
HOWEVER...

00:06:25.879 --> 00:06:28.582
FIRST I'LL NEED
TO WEAKEN THE PHARAOH,

00:06:28.582 --> 00:06:32.519
PREPARE HIM
FOR THE DAY I TAKE
MY ULTIMATE PRIZE.

00:06:32.519 --> 00:06:34.488
HEH HEH HEH!

00:06:34.488 --> 00:06:37.824
SIR, SHALL I ORDER
A TEAM OF RARE HUNTERS

00:06:37.824 --> 00:06:40.260
TO PAY KAIBA
A LITTLE VISIT?

00:06:40.260 --> 00:06:42.529
[ALOUD]
NO. LEAVE KAIBA
TO HIS GAMES.

00:06:42.529 --> 00:06:45.499
I HAVE A MORE
IMPORTANT TASK
TO TEND TO FIRST.

00:06:45.499 --> 00:06:49.570
DISPATCH ARKANA
TO TAKE DOWN YUGI MOTO!

00:06:49.570 --> 00:06:50.837
YES, SIR.

00:06:58.571 --> 00:07:01.074
Tristan: OK, SERENITY.
I'LL SEE YOU LATER.

00:07:01.074 --> 00:07:02.075
HMM?

00:07:02.075 --> 00:07:03.176
I'M GONNA GO DOWN

00:07:03.176 --> 00:07:05.044
AND SEE HOW YUGI
AND JOEY ARE DOING. BYE.

00:07:05.044 --> 00:07:06.679
UM...
HUH?

00:07:06.679 --> 00:07:08.548
TRISTAN, WILL YOU
PROMISE ME SOMETHING?

00:07:08.548 --> 00:07:09.649
SURE.

00:07:09.649 --> 00:07:10.917
WILL YOU TAKE ME
DOWNTOWN

00:07:10.917 --> 00:07:12.118
TO THE BATTLE CITY
TOURNAMENT

00:07:12.118 --> 00:07:14.354
ON THE DAY THAT I GET
MY BANDAGES REMOVED?

00:07:14.354 --> 00:07:15.622
TO BATTLE CITY?

00:07:15.622 --> 00:07:17.423
YEAH. IT'S REALLY
IMPORTANT TO ME

00:07:17.423 --> 00:07:19.259
THAT THE FIRST SIGHT
I SEE

00:07:19.259 --> 00:07:20.893
IS MY BROTHER JOEY
DUELING.

00:07:20.893 --> 00:07:22.562
IT WOULD BE
MY HONOR.

00:07:22.562 --> 00:07:24.030
AHH!

00:07:24.030 --> 00:07:25.098
CATCH YOU LATER.

00:07:25.098 --> 00:07:27.767
Tea: THAT WAS
AN AWESOME DUEL, JOEY.

00:07:27.767 --> 00:07:28.868
YEAH.

00:07:28.868 --> 00:07:30.136
I'M IMPRESSED
BY HOW MUCH

00:07:30.136 --> 00:07:31.904
YOUR DUELING SKILLS
HAVE IMPROVED.

00:07:31.904 --> 00:07:33.373
THANKS A LOT,
GRAMPS.

00:07:33.373 --> 00:07:36.042
WELL, WE'RE OFF
TO FIND YUGI.

00:07:36.042 --> 00:07:37.410
OK. LATER.

00:07:37.410 --> 00:07:38.611
GOOD LUCK!

00:07:43.416 --> 00:07:45.718
Yugi: I'M GLAD JOEY
LET US HANG ON

00:07:45.718 --> 00:07:47.587
TO HIS RED EYES
BLACK DRAGON.

00:07:47.587 --> 00:07:48.888
THAT'S HIS FAVORITE CARD.

00:07:48.888 --> 00:07:49.956
AND NOW THAT WE HAVE IT,

00:07:49.956 --> 00:07:52.458
IT'S LIKE HIS HEART'S
IN OUR DECK.

00:07:52.458 --> 00:07:55.194
NO MATTER WHERE WE ARE,
JOEY WILL BE WITH US.

00:07:55.194 --> 00:07:56.663
AND IF WE HAVE
TO FACE MARIK

00:07:56.663 --> 00:07:58.031
AND HIS ARMY
OF RARE HUNTERS,

00:07:58.031 --> 00:08:00.466
WE'RE GOING TO NEED
ALL THE SUPPORT WE CAN GET.

00:08:00.466 --> 00:08:03.102
I JUST HOPE THAT JOEY
CAN SURVIVE THE TOURNAMENT

00:08:03.102 --> 00:08:04.404
WITHOUT HIS RED EYES.

00:08:04.404 --> 00:08:05.505
HE CAN.

00:08:05.505 --> 00:08:06.839
JOEY IS A GREAT DUELIST,

00:08:06.839 --> 00:08:09.942
AND HE SEEMS TO GET BETTER
WITH EVERY DUEL HE FIGHTS.

00:08:09.942 --> 00:08:11.944
HE JUST HAS TO KEEP
BELIEVING IN HIMSELF.

00:08:11.944 --> 00:08:14.013
YEAH, JOEY HAS COME
A REALLY LONG WAY

00:08:14.013 --> 00:08:15.248
SINCE HIS FIRST DUEL.

00:08:15.248 --> 00:08:17.116
AND HE JUST
DEFEATED ESPA ROBA

00:08:17.116 --> 00:08:19.152
WITHOUT NEEDING
HIS RED EYES.

00:08:19.152 --> 00:08:21.054
MAYBE <i>WE</i> NEED
JOEY'S CARD

00:08:21.054 --> 00:08:23.556
TO HELP SAVE
THE WORLD FROM EVIL.

00:08:23.556 --> 00:08:24.957
OH!

00:08:24.957 --> 00:08:26.426
[THINKING]
SPEAKING OF EVIL,

00:08:26.426 --> 00:08:28.461
HOW WILL WE KNOW WHERE
MARIK WILL STRIKE NEXT?

00:08:28.461 --> 00:08:30.630
WE STILL DON'T EVEN KNOW
WHAT HE LOOKS LIKE!

00:08:30.630 --> 00:08:32.098
[LAUGHTER]
HMM?

00:08:32.098 --> 00:08:33.533
WHO ARE YOU?

00:08:33.533 --> 00:08:36.135
[CHUCKLES]

00:08:36.135 --> 00:08:39.138
HELLO, YUGI. WE'VE
BEEN LOOKING FOR YOU.

00:08:39.138 --> 00:08:40.673
HMM? WHO'S "WE"?

00:08:40.673 --> 00:08:43.076
YOU'LL FIND OUT
IF YOU WALK THAT WAY.

00:08:43.076 --> 00:08:46.179
53 STEPS FORWARD
AND INTO THAT TENT.

00:08:46.179 --> 00:08:49.982
MY MASTER IS WAITING
FOR YOU INSIDE.

00:08:49.982 --> 00:08:52.719
IT'S IN YOUR BEST
INTEREST TO GO.

00:08:52.719 --> 00:08:54.520
[LAUGHS]

00:08:55.988 --> 00:08:58.424
STILL NO SIGN
OF YUGI.

00:08:58.424 --> 00:08:59.959
HEY!

00:08:59.959 --> 00:09:01.060
THERE HE IS,
RIGHT THERE!

00:09:01.060 --> 00:09:02.061
WHERE?

00:09:04.097 --> 00:09:05.465
YUGI!

00:09:07.133 --> 00:09:08.968
I'M GETTING
TOO OLD FOR THIS!

00:09:08.968 --> 00:09:10.937
HMM...

00:09:10.937 --> 00:09:13.272
THERE'S NO ONE HERE.

00:09:13.272 --> 00:09:14.741
MAGIC SHOW?

00:09:14.741 --> 00:09:16.442
[LAUGHING]

00:09:16.442 --> 00:09:17.844
ENTER HERE, YUGI.

00:09:17.844 --> 00:09:20.346
MY MASTER'S WAITING.

00:09:23.416 --> 00:09:25.651
WHERE'D HE GO?

00:09:25.651 --> 00:09:26.686
OH!

00:09:26.686 --> 00:09:27.687
THERE HE IS!

00:09:27.687 --> 00:09:28.788
YUGI?

00:09:28.788 --> 00:09:30.757
IT'S ALMOST LIKE
HE'S IN A TRANCE!

00:09:33.059 --> 00:09:34.060
Both: YUGI!

00:09:36.729 --> 00:09:37.764
AAH!
AAH!

00:09:37.764 --> 00:09:39.399
HE'S TRAPPED
IN THERE!

00:09:39.399 --> 00:09:42.635
OH, YUGI!

00:09:42.635 --> 00:09:45.138
YUGI!
YUGI, WHERE ARE YOU?

00:09:45.138 --> 00:09:46.439
OH, NO,
HE'S GONE!

00:09:47.974 --> 00:09:49.075
Mokuba:
THAT'S WEIRD.

00:09:49.075 --> 00:09:50.309
SETO!

00:09:50.309 --> 00:09:51.377
HMM?

00:09:51.377 --> 00:09:52.812
THE TOURNAMENT
SURVEILLANCE SYSTEM

00:09:52.812 --> 00:09:54.580
JUST LOST TRACK
OF YUGI MOTO!

00:09:54.580 --> 00:09:55.748
HE'S DISAPPEARED!

00:09:55.748 --> 00:09:56.816
HE'S DISAPPEARED?

00:09:56.816 --> 00:09:58.985
IMPOSSIBLE!

00:09:58.985 --> 00:10:01.988
MAKE SURE
THE SATELLITE LINK
IS WORKING, NOW.

00:10:01.988 --> 00:10:02.989
MMM.

00:10:05.358 --> 00:10:08.861
[THINKING]
YUGI'S DUEL DISC SENDS OUT
A CONSTANT I.D. SIGNAL,

00:10:08.861 --> 00:10:10.396
SO WHEREVER HE IS,

00:10:10.396 --> 00:10:12.498
HIS SIGNAL'S BEING
BLOCKED SOMEHOW.

00:10:12.498 --> 00:10:14.033
BUT I'LL FIND HIM.

00:10:25.244 --> 00:10:26.913
WHERE AM I?

00:10:26.913 --> 00:10:28.381
HUH?

00:10:28.381 --> 00:10:30.883
Computer: HACKING
INTO BATTLE CITY DATABASE.

00:10:30.883 --> 00:10:34.720
DUELIST PROFILE
FOR YUGI MOTO.

00:10:34.720 --> 00:10:36.956
DUELING LEVEL:
5 STARS.

00:10:36.956 --> 00:10:39.759
RAREST CARD:
DARK MAGICIAN.

00:10:41.561 --> 00:10:43.362
MY DARK MAGICIAN!

00:10:47.266 --> 00:10:48.501
[LAUGHING]

00:10:48.501 --> 00:10:50.069
I'VE BEEN WAITING
FOR YOU.

00:10:50.069 --> 00:10:52.705
YOU ARE NOT WORTHY
OF HAVING ME
IN YOUR DECK,

00:10:52.705 --> 00:10:56.909
SO PREPARE TO LOSE ME
FOREVER.

00:10:56.909 --> 00:10:58.511
YOU'RE NOT THE ONLY
DUELIST WITH MY POWER

00:10:58.511 --> 00:10:59.912
IN THEIR DECK, YUGI,

00:10:59.912 --> 00:11:01.747
AND YOU'RE CERTAINLY
NOT THE BEST.

