HUH?

00:12:48.649 --> 00:12:49.716
WHAT DO YOU MEAN,

00:12:49.716 --> 00:12:51.652
YOU HAVE ORDERS
FROM YOUR SUPERIORS?

00:12:51.652 --> 00:12:55.155
JUST WHO IS IT THAT YOU'RE
WORKING FOR, ARKANA?

