I'LL CUT YOUR DECK.

00:14:04.758 --> 00:14:06.560
OF COURSE.

00:14:06.560 --> 00:14:08.462
YOU KNOW, THERE
IS AN OLD SAYING

00:14:08.462 --> 00:14:10.898
AMONG HIGH-ROLLERS
AND CARD SHARKS:

00:14:10.898 --> 00:14:12.966
"ALWAYS TRUST
YOUR OPPONENTS,

00:14:12.966 --> 00:14:15.102
BUT ONLY AFTER YOU'VE
CUT THEIR DECK."

00:14:15.102 --> 00:14:16.670
HEH!

