AN EXTRA DOWN SIDE
TO LOSING.

00:14:32.085 --> 00:14:34.087
HUH?

00:14:34.087 --> 00:14:35.289
GET READY!

00:14:35.289 --> 00:14:36.823
THE SHOW--
I MEAN, DUEL--

00:14:36.823 --> 00:14:39.326
