NO!

00:14:42.062 --> 00:14:43.530
RELAX.

00:14:43.530 --> 00:14:45.098
WE'RE BOTH LOCKED IN,

00:14:45.098 --> 00:14:47.167
WHICH MEANS NEITHER
OF US CAN ESCAPE.

