SEE, THERE'S
AN EXTRA TWIST.

00:14:50.270 --> 00:14:52.606
WE'RE NOT JUST
PLAYING FOR WHAT'S
INSIDE YOUR DECK,

00:14:52.606 --> 00:14:54.675
