WHAT'S THAT?

00:14:59.546 --> 00:15:02.749
[LAUGHS]

00:15:02.749 --> 00:15:05.118
IT'S A DARK ENERGY
DISC, YUGI,

00:15:05.118 --> 00:15:07.354
AND I WOULDN'T GET
TOO CLOSE.

00:15:07.354 --> 00:15:10.891
ONE TOUCH,
AND YOUR MIND'S BANISHED
TO THE SHADOW REALM!

00:15:16.423 --> 00:15:17.924
DON'T WORRY, YUGI.

