GETS TO US!

00:15:31.805 --> 00:15:33.006
PRECISELY!

00:15:33.006 --> 00:15:35.508
AND THEN YOU CAN SAY HELLO
TO THE SHADOW REALM!

00:15:35.508 --> 00:15:38.344
ALL RIGHT. NOW LOOK
DOWN BETWEEN YOU FEET.

00:15:38.344 --> 00:15:42.282
YOU'LL SEE EACH OF US
HAS A KEY BOX.

