YES, AND INSIDE
IS A KEY

00:15:46.419 --> 00:15:49.589
TO UNLOCK THE SHACKLES
AROUND YOUR LEGS.

00:15:49.589 --> 00:15:52.759
YOUR BOX DISPLAYS
YOUR OPPONENT'S LIFE POINTS

00:15:52.759 --> 00:15:55.695
AND WILL ONLY OPEN
IF YOU WIN THE DUEL!

00:15:55.695 --> 00:15:57.497
[LAUGHS]

00:15:57.497 --> 00:16:00.767
ONLY THEN CAN YOU
SAVE YOURSELF!

00:16:00.767 --> 00:16:02.402
YOU'RE INSANE!

00:16:02.402 --> 00:16:04.404
THINK OF IT
AS A HOPE CHEST, REALLY,

00:16:04.404 --> 00:16:07.841
BECAUSE THAT KEY
IS YOUR ONLY HOPE.

