NO. I'M A MAN
WHO'S UNDEFEATED.

00:16:20.386 --> 00:16:21.855
NOT FOR LONG,
ARKANA!

00:16:21.855 --> 00:16:23.123
HA!

00:16:23.123 --> 00:16:24.724
YOU'VE MET
YOUR MATCH,

00:16:24.724 --> 00:16:26.426
SO GET READY!

