RIGHT ON TOP

00:17:23.983 --> 00:17:25.652
WHEN YUGI CUT MY DECK,

00:17:25.652 --> 00:17:29.155
EXACTLY AS I PLANNED
IT WOULD.

00:17:29.155 --> 00:17:31.324
NOW YUGI WILL LEARN
HOW DANGEROUS IT IS

00:17:31.324 --> 00:17:33.793
TO PLAY GAMES
WITH A MAGICIAN,

